dc_description_s: This data represents trails for Jefferson County, Wisconsin in 2019. [Classification Codes: Stress: MHS = High/Med volume/stress routes; LS= Low volume/stress routes; OFFRD= Off road routes on either paved or crushed stone pathsTrails: GRT = Glacial River Trail; GDT= Glacial Drumlin Trail; IAT = Ice Age Trail; CR= City Routes; CRR= County Rural Routes; ICR = Intra-Community RouteRoad Ranking: RSG = Road suitable for shared bike/motor vehicle use; RSF= Road may be suitable depending on cyclist's skill level; RSP = Road not recommended for biking in current condition(2012). Also to icluded known snowmobile trails aquired by GPS and other means.]
